{"tid":168511,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[又死1隻]婦上山採茶遭箭射死　獵者：以為是野豬","createTime":"2017-03-23T14:56:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-23T16:41:04.000Z","uid":32407,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"28601e6dcb5342d52b70c3114e3111adc2be20cf","tid":168511,"uid":32407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T14:56:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170323/bkncn-20170323090219748-0323_05011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fcn%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170323%2Fbkncn-20170323090219748-0323_05011_001.html&d=ilevQ%2FkIXqJInDdlQ9M4eMmB%2BETtKD6oVAJ%2Bxq8xWyI%3D&h=0695d217\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/cn/bkn/cnt/news/20170323/bkncn-20170323090219748-0323_05011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n江蘇南京江寧區朱門社區湯村，一位67歲的魏姓老婦上周二在山中採茶時，被一名捕獵野味的男子當成誤的成野豬，遭對方一箭射穿心臟，老婦當場傷重死亡。目前，警方已將涉事男子抓獲，及處刑事拘留，案件正在進一步調查中。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，朱門社區的山中有盛產一種野生山茶，據稱喝了能治高血壓、高血脂，老婦過去亦曾到山中採摘這種山茶，一般從早上出發，下午5時左右便回到家中。事發當日，老婦早上7時左右便帶同工具離家登山，惟其家人等至入黑，仍未見老婦未歸來，開始擔心老婦是出了意外。當晚，老婦的家人與其他村民到山上搜索，結果一無所獲，只好報警求助。警方翌日在山上發現老婦的遺體，並抓獲一名涉案男子。<br />\n<br />\n警方表示，涉事的男子30歲左右，是附近一間企業的保安。事發當日，男子帶同弓箭到山上打獵，在行至山上某處時發現了兩隻野豬，惟野豬見人就跑，男子隨即尾隨追獵。期間，男子忽然發現一處草叢中有動靜，遂立即引弓射去，不料就因此誤中了老婦，且一箭穿心。老婦中箭後未幾已斷氣死亡，男子發現自己闖下大禍，隨後向警方投案自首。"},{"pid":"1ce29e89305c6abdb1d9f9384dc394594a9127d4","tid":168511,"uid":6903,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:02:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">男子發現自己闖下大禍，隨後向警方投案自首。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14f1c232a3db990f42d29813aa0f0fcbe675830f","tid":168511,"uid":12618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:04:35.000Z","msg":"唔係野豬 係野雞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67ec3f33c03cd814bdf2ffdcb653bf5ecdf102b4","tid":168511,"uid":10438,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:08:42.000Z","msg":"保安"},{"pid":"4d66dad83bfb2767102ff8128901b41494008e5f","tid":168511,"uid":83052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:10:09.000Z","msg":"咩年代<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e198d1e25d47f6b88fbb6efca0938aa7cd8d79c0","tid":168511,"uid":90045,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T15:32:28.000Z","msg":"啲箭咁撚勁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e0c4025fce85291b47dc3ea16361743b245e866","tid":168511,"uid":45148,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T16:41:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><span style=\"color: red;\">男子發現自己闖下大禍，隨後向警方投案自首。</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n雖然食野味生番<br />\n但自首就有番d人性<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}